Author: put_thelotion
Text: I know candids are really hit or miss for “cute accident” or “sewer gremlin” but this one also just hurt because it happened from a food focused event so I’m like. deliberating over vegetables and I just hate it  the page got back to me quickly though and cropped me out of the photo so I’m happy :)

Author: not_the_cicada
Text: Oh shit I’m so sorry, that sucks. My uni has giant posters on buildings and campus pr would come around and take pics occasionally and I was always TERRIFIED that one day I would see a 20’ tall version of myself on a building 😂😬  Candid pics are weird, you catch people looking really funny when they aren’t posing. I’m sure you look bomb, don’t trust your own eyes :P
